description: Deregisters tag keys to prevent tags that have the specified tag keys from being included in scheduled event notifications for resources in the Region.

parameters.name: InstanceTagAttribute
parameters.description: Information about the tag keys to deregister. IncludeAllTagsOfInstance (boolean) --- Indicates whether to deregister all tag keys in the current Region. Specify false to deregister all tag keys. InstanceTagKeys (list) --- Information about the tag keys to deregister. (string) ---

nested_params.name: IncludeAllTagsOfInstance
nested_params.description: Indicates whether to deregister all tag keys in the current Region. Specify false to deregister all tag keys.

nested_params.name: InstanceTagKeys
nested_params.description: Information about the tag keys to deregister.

nested_items.name: InstanceTagAttribute
nested_items.description: The resulting set of tag keys.

nested_items.name: IncludeAllTagsOfInstance
nested_items.description: Indicates wheter all tag keys in the current Region are registered to appear in scheduled event notifications. true indicates that all tag keys in the current Region are registered.
